IMPORTANT NOTE:

This package is a public wrapper that provides installation and access to the
proprietary NimbusSDKCore package. While this wrapper code is MIT-licensed,
the NimbusSDKCore package itself is commercial software requiring a paid license.

- NimbusSDK (this package): MIT License (open source)
- NimbusSDKCore (installed separately): Commercial License (proprietary)

To use the full functionality, you must:
1. Purchase a license at https://nimbusbci.com
2. Obtain an API key
3. Install the proprietary core: NimbusSDK.install_core("your-api-key")

See https://nimbusbci.com for licensing options and pricing.

